y.",Gw="Failed deleting policy.",Vw="Delete {policy}?",Kw="Detach the policy from users, groups, or roles in your account.",Bw="Your policy exceeds the non-whitespace character limit of {size}.",Yw="Error with policy.",Hw="The character limit includes the total character count of all inline policies for {principalId}.",qw="Use the JSON editor for more information about the character count.",jw="Review and save",$w="Please fix all policy syntax errors before continuing",Qw="Policy {policyName} updated.",Jw="Policy {policyName} created.",Xw="Policy {policyName} updated with a few errors. See error description below.",Zw="Add permissions by selecting services, actions, resources, and conditions. Build permission statements using the JSON editor.",eC="Info about policy permissions",tC="Show remaining.",aC="This policy does not grant any permissions. To grant access, policies must have an action that has an applicable resource or condition. For details, choose",sC="Description - <i>optional</i>",iC="Policy version to replace",oC="This policy already has the maximum of 5 versions. Saving changes to this policy will create a new version replacing the oldest non-default policy version (version {versionId} - created {dateCreated})",rC="Set this new version as the default.",nC="Permissions defined in this version will be applied to all the entities this policy is attached to.",cC="Creation time",lC="Entities attached",uC="Policy versions",dC="Last Accessed",pC="Info about Policies",mC="Failed to create new instance profile for role.",hC="Failed to add role to instance profile: {instanceProfileName}",yC="Select trusted entity",gC="Info about Trusted Entity Types for Roles",vC="Info about Role Permissions",fC="Name, review, and create",AC="This trust policy contains invalid JSON syntax. Fix JSON syntax to proceed.",SC="Create a custom trust policy to enable others to perform actions in this account.",EC="Set permissions boundary - <i>optional</i>",IC="AWS service",wC="Allow AWS